.TH "libnvme_ns_compare" 9 "libnvme_ns_compare" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvme_ns_compare \- Compare data on a namespace
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" libnvme_ns_compare
.BI "(libnvme_ns_t n "  ","
.BI "void *buf "  ","
.BI "off_t offset "  ","
.BI "size_t count "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "n" 12
Namespace instance
.IP "buf" 12
Buffer with data to be compared
.IP "offset" 12
LBA offset of \fIn\fP
.IP "count" 12
Number of sectors in \fIbuf\fP
.SH "RETURN"
Number of sectors compared
